title: Looking for JNG/SUPPORT for Clash
body:
Looking for somebody to play either jungle or support their choice, preferably in high silver to gold.
> Add me 'AgentPotato" and **COMMENT** in this post so I can be certain with the requests.

Discord link will also be provided for team communication.
We also would like to play a few games beforehand to synergize well.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}  {{sticker:sg-ahri-2}} {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
